## 📌 The Problem

Small independent grocery stores lose thousands of dollars each year to spoilage, stockouts, and manual inventory errors. Most owners track stock with pen and paper or basic spreadsheets — with no alerts, no intelligence, and no time to analyse trends.

**SmartStock** gives store managers instant visibility into their inventory: what's running low, what's about to expire, and what to reorder — all in one dashboard.

---

## ✨ Key Features

| Screen | What It Does |
|--------|-------------|
| 🏠 **Dashboard** | At-a-glance overview: low stock alerts, expiring items, fast-moving products, and an AI reorder suggestion banner |
| 📋 **Inventory List** | Full product list with search, category filter, and sort by quantity or expiry date |
| ➕ **Add / Edit Product** | Create or update product records with full CRUD functionality |
| 🚨 **Alerts** | Centralized alert screen with urgency labels and AI-generated reorder suggestions |
| 🔍 **Product Detail** | Full product profile with quick quantity update and simulated quantity history |

