## 🤖 How AI Was Used

- **Claude.ai** — Architecture planning, data model design, requirements development, and README generation
- **ChatGPT** — Ideation, feature brainstorming, and sample data generation
- **Replit AI Agent** — Screen-by-screen code generation, routing setup, state management, and UI polish

No prior programming experience was required. The AI acted as the developer; the team acted as product managers and architects.

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** React, React Router, CSS
- **State Management:** React Context API + useState
- **Persistence:** localStorage (browser-based)
- **Development Platform:** Replit.com
- **AI Tools:** Claude.ai, ChatGPT, Replit AI Agent
- **Version Control:** GitHub

---

## 🚀 Getting Started
```bash
git clone https://github.com/abdulkhan-14/smartstock.git
cd smartstock
npm install
npm run dev
```

> **Note:** The app seeds 20 sample grocery products into localStorage on first launch.

